<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0335: Crankshaft Position Sensor “A” Circuit
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Any one of the following error counters related to CKP sensor signal is more than specified number with engine running.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Displaced gap by one tooth or more
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Detection of gap at missing gap range
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Faulty distance between gaps
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CKP sensor signal is not inputted while CMP sensor signal is being inputted.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(Type A and C: 3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(Type B: 2 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
CKP sensor and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Sensor plate
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
